# Rust
target/
**/*.rs.bk
# Cargo.lock is committed — nexo-rs is a binary application (Rust
# ecosystem convention). Reproducible builds in CI + `--locked` in
# the release workflow depend on it.

# Secrets — never commit
secrets/*
!secrets/.gitkeep
!secrets/*.example
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.key
*.pem
*.nkey

# Runtime data
data/
logs/
# Cache of resolved peer devices per JID. Contains contacts' phone
# numbers (PII) and only makes sense for a specific paired account.
device_cache.json
# Local dev artifacts
screenshot.png
*.patch

# Agent runtime logs
agent.log
*.log

# Private agent definitions (business prompts, pricing, internal contacts).
# Runtime loads `config/agents.d/*.yaml` and merges them with the base
# `agents.yaml`. Keep the base file public-safe; put anything sensitive
# (customer-facing sales scripts, tarifarios, etc.) into the drop-in dir.
config/agents.d/*.yaml
!config/agents.d/*.example.yaml

# IDE
.idea/
.vscode/

# Claude Code local worktrees + runtime artifacts
.claude/worktrees/
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
.claude/projects/

# mdBook build output — published via GitHub Actions, not committed
docs/book/
_site/
docs/theme/highlight.css.bak
*.swp
*.swo

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
